-- libm math externs (native/LLVM only): exercises both emitNumExtern arms —
-- one-arg (sqrt/cos/floor) and two-arg (pow/hypot).  eval routes through the
-- runtime.mdk externs so `run` matches this build-path golden exactly.
-- 4.0 + 1.0 + 3.0 + 8.0 + 5.0 = 21.0
main = sqrt 16.0 + cos 0.0 + floor 3.7 + pow 2.0 3.0 + hypot 3.0 4.0
